flowchart TD
    A[Initialize BooleanGameEnv] --> B[Create one TabularIQLAgent per PettingZoo agent]
    B --> C[Reset env and get initial observations]
    C --> D[Encode global assignment to tabular state index]
    D --> E[Each agent picks epsilon-greedy action index]
    E --> F[Decode action index to MultiBinary action vector]
    F --> G[Parallel step joint actions in env]
    G --> H[Receive next observations and per-agent rewards]
    H --> I[Encode next state index]
    I --> J[Per-agent Q update]
    J --> K{Episode done?}
    K -- No --> D
    K -- Yes --> L[Start next episode]
    L --> C

    M[After training: greedy rollout] --> N[Select argmax Q action per agent]
    N --> O[Step env and print rewards/final assignment]
